snippet.title: D.A.M. Champion 2nd Game Trailer
snippet.description:
This video is the 2nd trailer for the indie monster taming game known as D.A.M. Champion. A game franchise created by one person with a passion for the genre.

#monstertaming #damchampion  #creaturecollector 

The OFC Media is The YouTube Channel to discover games like Pokemon or similar to Pokemon within the monster taming genre

Join The Community
https://www.youtube.com/@TheOFCMedia?sub_confirmation=1
